Description: Web-based Squid proxy statistics and monitoring dashboard
 SquidStats is a Flask web application that provides real-time analysis
 and statistics for Squid proxy servers, including user monitoring,
 bandwidth tracking, access log analysis, and reporting.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time user monitoring and bandwidth statistics
  - Access log analysis with filtering and PDF export
  - ACL and blacklist domain management
  - LDAP/Active Directory authentication integration
  - Per-user and per-group quota management
  - Telegram bot notifications
  - Multi-language support (English and Spanish)
  - Database support: SQLite, PostgreSQL, MariaDB/MySQL
  - Backup and restore functionality
